>\n自問體弱多病出街成日都會戴口罩(一病就好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩三個星期先好)<br />\n搞下搞下全家出門口個陣都帶口罩旁身"},{"pid":"66c09f32447734af3768fea5ae904cd44a1ad01d","tid":880954,"uid":114148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"375cc7bbd4316309869b33a7b14aa18282b348d5","tid":880954,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"特別係人多但人流慢嘅地方例如地鐵, 圖書館...係咁重痰咳, 流鼻涕<br />\n<br />\n反而好似唔少人驚比人傳染而自己戴, 社會公共衛生意識係咪本末倒置?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"勁嗡"},{"pid":"9e4c9a2a5fc5f6b239b8549805cdae007985fa53","tid":880954,"uid":20238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"好似話病咗戴口罩對個病人都係好事嚟，唔係有機會會交叉感染，影響病情"},{"pid":"965feefe37405d5b166bb8b39c638f3e5ee7eb67","tid":880954,"uid":43117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"以前返工有個陷家鏟間中不停咁咳<br />\n叫佢戴罩又話未有人病唔撚戴<br />\n睇住佢日日飲凍飲 屌你老母咳仲飲凍野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5801fd646d24c0a029506ac25894299b21a72968","tid":880954,"uid":119478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af63d00fa9d15341774d1c52c47d53b819ce0132","tid":880954,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"買唔方便?一買就成盒,唔係嚴重都好少地方有單賣<br />\n戴又唔舒服又係,焗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"無話唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流感高峰期 一盒要清可以清得好快<br />\n一盒50個 放最多3年先過期<br />\n點都會清晒啦 同埋一盒買平好多好多<br />\n<br />\n單買便利店多數有 3蚊一個<br />\n(我覺得)鐵線又鬆個mask又焗 唔貼面<br />\n不過應急ok<br />\n<br />\n成盒買通常去藥房/醫院復康店<br />\n復康店通常要覆診紙先比你買 同埋成日無貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舒唔舒服睇人<br />\n可能我戴太多慣晒"},{"pid":"0c738b3a364d511071ecbecc500b58f1daa6d39a","tid":880954,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4c9a2a5fc5f6b239b8549805cdae007985fa53","tid":880954,"uid":20238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"好似話病咗戴口罩對個病人都係好事嚟，唔係有機會會交叉感染，影響病情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"巴打good reminder<br />\n真係講起誤以為病咗唔可以再病"},{"pid":"fe180e9aee3024187032845168daec04bdd83597","tid":880954,"uid":165956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"衛生意識低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過唔只係香港人  邊個國家既人都係咁上下<br />\n我最近都開始帶口罩食維C   見作病 頭開始痛攝親就沖定d念慈x葛根湯打定底 會無咁易病"},{"pid":"f2e0d6c843c1702855e65d11434df9781f0440b3","tid":880954,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"因為唔記得沙士"},{"pid":"28fd0170d465d0f1951d33bdda3edaf1d3cfc6a1","tid":880954,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"自私"},{"pid":"be6ac9ccb78ed2b8457bd5ff62c61af44bdbd7a5","tid":880954,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"d 阿叔好多都唔戴 <br />\n<br />\n見過做人老母嘅，都唔識身教<br />\n自己同小朋友都咳<br />\n兩個都唔戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b175977e2b19397b90945eb5dfd2275f290376","tid":880954,"uid":29063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9c38b730b7599a913b64fa41a30171f0e6e1ecf","tid":880954,"uid":162316,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"開埋聲話佢地咳不如帶口罩 仲要話氣管敏感無事既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"氣管敏感唔會知自己幾時咳, 有時出街刺激下就會係咁咳, 轉頭就會冇事<br />\n<br />\n利申: 氣管敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d49afb7aa9c88d4d4b0a2bedafeac9b86b0c8c3","tid":880954,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b175977e2b19397b90945eb5dfd2275f290376","tid":880954,"uid":29063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9c38b730b7599a913b64fa41a30171f0e6e1ecf","tid":880954,"uid":162316,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"r